"""declare the variable meal and assign it the value 44.50
Create the variable tax and set it equal to the decimal value of 6.75%
Set the variable tip to decimal value of 15%
"""
meal = 44.50
tax = 6.75 / 100
tip = 15.0 / 100

#reassign meal to the value of itself + itself * tax
meal = meal + meal * tax
#Assign the variable total to the sum of meal + meal * tip
total = meal + meal * tip

#prints to the console the value of total with exactly two numbers after the decimal
print("%.2f" % total)
